(What it is) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(Float Plan Wizard is a ColdFusion + MySQL web app for creating, managing, and monitoring) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(   boating float plans. It combines plan authoring, contact sharing, check-in status, and overdue) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(   alerting in one workflow.) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
T*
(Who it is for) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(Primary persona: recreational or small-crew vessel operators/owners who need to document trips,) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(   passengers, routes, and emergency contacts before departure.) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
T*
(What it does) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Provides session-based login/logout and current-user session retrieval via API endpoints.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Lets users create, edit, clone, delete, send, and check in float plans.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Manages related entities: vessels, operators, passengers, contacts, waypoints, and home port.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Runs a multi-step wizard UI for plan basics, times/route, and plan details.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Generates a populated float plan PDF and supports sending plan emails to designated contacts.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Tracks monitoring states \(for example ACTIVE/OVERDUE\) and exposes monitored-plan data.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(- Includes marine/map support endpoints \(WMS proxy, marine POIs, navigation aids\) used by) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
T*
(  dashboard flows.) Tj
